reviewText: Please be careful when you order: there were 5 DVDs in the "complete second season" set. I only received one disc for $50, only 3 episodes, but it was still entitled "complete". Be sure every episode is named (only 3 were named, and since some episodes of the previous set were lenghthy and originally viewed as two, I didn't realize the problem) and that the offer says "5 DVD set". Haven't watched it, as I'm going to check into returning it.
